---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Profile from "../../assets/carissa.jpg";
import SvgLoader from "../../assets/SvgLoader.astro";
import Title from "../layouts/Title.astro";
import Text from "../layouts/Text.astro";
import SectionWrapper from "../layouts/SectionWrapper.astro";
import ButtonRoute from "../layouts/ButtonRoute.astro";
---

<script>
  import "@scripts/landing";
</script>

<SectionWrapper id="home">
  <div
    class="flex justify-center lg:items-start items-center lg:flex-row flex-col z-20 gap-16 lg:gap-0"
  >
    <!-- image container -->
    <div
      class="relative flex lg:justify-start justify-center items-star w-fullt min-w-[100px] max-w-[250px] md:max-w-[350px] lg:max-w-[350px] lg:max-h-max max-h-[600px]"
    >
      <Image
        src={Profile}
        alt="Carissa Ng"
        class="h-full aspect-[9/14] object-cover z-20"
      />
      <div class="absolute w-full h-full bg-red-200 opacity-10 z-10">
        <div
          id="l1"
          class="absolute -top-[12rem] -left-[10rem] w-3/4 -rotate-[35deg]"
        >
          <SvgLoader icon="grass" />
        </div>
        <div
          id="l2"
          class="absolute -bottom-[12rem] -left-[10rem] w-3/4 -rotate-[135deg]"
        >
          <SvgLoader icon="grass" />
        </div>
        <div
          id="l3"
          class="absolute -top-[12rem] -right-[10rem] w-3/4 rotate-[35deg]"
        >
          <SvgLoader icon="grass" />
        </div>
        <div
          id="l4"
          class="absolute -bottom-[12rem] -right-[8rem] w-3/5 rotate-[150deg]"
        >
          <SvgLoader icon="grass" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div
      class="flex flex-col gap-4 lg:pl-16 px-0 h-full relative lg:items-start items-center"
    >
      <Title>Welcome! I’m <span class="italic">Carissa.</span></Title>
      <h3
        class="text-ng-primary-darker tracking-[0.2em] lg:tracking-[0.2em] text-sm lg:text-md font-[400] leading-8 lg:text-left text-center"
      >
        PSYCHOTHERAPIST | RP #13283
      </h3>
      <Text>
        I’m so glad you’re here. Maybe you’re navigating conflict in your
        relationships, experiencing symptoms of depression and anxiety, or
        struggling to process your emotions. Whatever your reason for being
        here, my hope is to provide a secure base from which you can be more
        grounded in who you are and your story, feel closer to the people you
        care about, and cultivate a life that feels more aligned with your
        values.
      </Text>
      <Text>
        Life is complex and unpredictable, so it would be my deepest privilege
        to join you in your journey as we work together to move through life’s
        challenges and navigate where you would like to go next.
      </Text>
      <ButtonRoute link="#about"> MORE ABOUT ME </ButtonRoute>
    </div>
  </div>
</SectionWrapper>
